              { text: "$\Theta(g(n))$ = { f(n) : ∃ c₁, c₂, $n_{0} > 0$, ∀$n \geq n_{0}$ : $0 \leq c_{1}g(n) \leq f(n)$ ≤ c₂g(n) }", indent: 1, note: "식 3.1 — tight bound" },
