                    explain: "CLRS p.467 계산. 확장 시 $size_i = 2$·size_{i−1} = 2·num_{i−1}. Φ_i = 2·num_i − 2·num_{i−1} = 2. Φ_{i−1} = 2·num_{i−1} − num_{i−1} = num_{i−1}. $c_i = num_${i−1} + 1. ĉ_i = num_{i−1}+1 + 2 − num_{i−1} = 3." },
